tool_description: An API Service returning fun facts about cats.

api_list.name: Get all facts about cat
api_list.description: This endpoint returns all available fact about cats in our database.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cat-facts12.p.rapidapi.com/AllFacts"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cat-facts12.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
